      "html": "<div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Andoni Llamazares</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\">ὁ</span>  <span data-text=\"δᾶμος\">δᾶμος</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"τῶν\">τῶν</span> Λιλυβαιιτᾶν <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διόγνητον\n                    Δαματρίου Μήγαν\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διόγνητον\">Διόγνητον</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δαματρίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Δαματρίου\">Δαματρίου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Μήγαν\">Μήγα[ν]</span></span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"εὐεργέταν\">ε̣ὐ̣ε̣ρ̣γ̣έ̣τ̣α̣ν̣</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Andoni Llamazares</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\">Ο</span><span data-text=\"δᾶμος\">ΔΑΜΟΣ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"τῶν\">ΤΩΝ</span>ΛΙΛΥΒΑΙΙΤΑΝ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διόγνητον\n                    Δαματρίου Μήγαν\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διόγνητον\">ΔΙΟΓΝΗΤΟΝ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</spa